<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢١٤٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4972">عَيَّاشُ بْنُ الْوَلِيدِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3160">عَبْدُ الْأَعْلَى: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6279">مَعْمَرٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">الزُّهْرِيِّ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4397">عَطَاءِ بْنِ يَزِيدَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2313">أَبِي سَعِيدٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«نَهَى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنْ لِبْسَتَيْنِ وَعَنْ بَيْعَتَيْنِ: الْمُلَامَسَةِ وَالْمُنَابَذَةِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>